  "2.3.8 Cloze style": "2.3.8 填空样式",
  "Cancel cloze Style": "取消填空样式",
  "In this theme, you can use ==~~your words~~==, *==~~your words~~==* and *~~your words~~* to obtain a cloze-style, active this option to cancel it": "在此主题中，您可以使用 ==~~您的文字~~==、*==~~您的文字~~==* 和 *~~您的文字~~* 获得填空样式，激活此选项以取消它",
  "Cloze background color": "填空背景颜色",
  "Cloze Style One, i.e. ==~~your words~~==, hovering to find \"your words\", should declare \"cssclass：cloze\" in the YAML area if you want to use them in the Live Preview mode": "填空样式一，即 ==~~您的文字~~==，悬停以找到“您的文字”，如果要在实时预览模式下使用它们，应在 YAML 区域声明“cssclass：cloze”",
  "Underline decoration style": "下划线装饰样式",
  "Can type 'solid', 'dotted', 'dashed', 'wavy' or 'double' for Cloze Style One, i.e. ==~~your words~~==, hovering to find \"your words\", should declare \"cssclass：cloze\" in the YAML area if you want to use them in the Live Preview mode": "对于填空样式一，即 ==~~您的文字~~==，可以输入 'solid'、'dotted'、'dashed'、'wavy' 或 'double'，悬停以找到“您的文字”，如果要在实时预览模式下使用它们，应在 YAML 区域声明“cssclass：cloze”",
  "Underline decoration color": "下划线装饰颜色",
  "For Cloze Style One, i.e. ==~~your words~~==, hovering to find \"your words\", should declare 'cssclass：cloze' in the YAML area if you want to use them in the Live Preview mode": "对于填空样式一，即 ==~~您的文字~~==，悬停以找到“您的文字”，如果要在实时预览模式下使用它们，应在 YAML 区域声明 'cssclass：cloze'",
  "Underline decoration style for Cloze style TWO": "填空样式二的下划线装饰样式",
  "Can type 'solid', 'dotted', 'dashed', 'wavy', 'double' or 'none' for Cloze Style TWO, i.e. *==~~your words~~==*, pressing down the primary mouse button to find \"your words\", should declare 'cssclass：cloze' in the YAML area if you want to use them in the Live Preview mode": "对于填空样式二，即 *==~~您的文字~~==*，可以输入 'solid'、'dotted'、'dashed'、'wavy'、'double' 或 'none'，按下鼠标主键以找到“您的文字”，如果要在实时预览模式下使用它们，应在 YAML 区域声明 'cssclass：cloze'",
  "Underline decoration color for Cloze style TWO": "填空样式二的下划线装饰颜色",
  "For Cloze Style TWO, i.e. *==~~your words~~==*, pressing down the primary mouse button to find \"your words\", should declare 'cssclass：cloze' in the YAML area if you want to use them in the Live Preview mode": "对于填空样式二，即 *==~~您的文字~~==*，按下鼠标主键以找到“您的文字”，如果要在实时预览模式下使用它们，应在 YAML 区域声明 'cssclass：cloze'",
  "Underline decoration style for Cloze style THREE (*~~your words~~*)": "填空样式三的下划线装饰样式 (*~~您的文字~~*)",
  "Can type 'solid', 'dotted', 'dashed', 'wavy', 'double' or 'none' for Cloze Style THREE, i.e. *~~your words~~*, pressing down the primary mouse button to find \"your words\", should declare 'cssclass：cloze' in the YAML area if you want to use them in the Live Preview mode": "对于填空样式三，即 *~~您的文字~~*，可以输入 'solid'、'dotted'、'dashed'、'wavy'、'double' 或 'none'，按下鼠标主键以找到“您的文字”，如果要在实时预览模式下使用它们，应在 YAML 区域声明 'cssclass：cloze'",
  "Underline decoration color for Cloze style THREE": "填空样式三的下划线装饰颜色",
  "For Cloze Style THREE, i.e. *~~your words~~*, pressing down the primary mouse button to find \"your words\", should declare 'cssclass：cloze' in the YAML area if you want to use them in the Live Preview mode": "对于填空样式三，即*~~你的词语~~*，按住鼠标主键查找“你的词语”，若要在实时预览模式下使用它们，应在YAML区域声明'cssclass：cloze'",
